{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/runviewer/issues/19/comments/45066181.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/labscript_suite/runviewer/issues/19#comment-45066181"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/runviewer/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/runviewer.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/labscript_suite/runviewer"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{71215673-ad3e-425c-ae04-84cc6c2ca7da}ts=445022"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "runviewer", "full_name": "labscript_suite/runviewer", "uuid": "{71215673-ad3e-425c-ae04-84cc6c2ca7da}"}, "title": "reset time axis button doesn't work if plot view is scrolled down"}, "content": {"raw": "Fixes #19\n\nMoved the \"hidden_plot\" (which actually needs to be always visible) so that the reset time axis button always works, even when you have a large number of plots visible and you have scrolled down the list.\n\n\u2192 <<cset 28c050d6343f>>", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Fixes <a href=\"#!/labscript_suite/runviewer/issues/19/reset-time-axis-button-doesnt-work-if-plot\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"reset time axis button doesn&#39;t work if plot view is scrolled down\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#19</s></a></p>\n<p>Moved the \"hidden_plot\" (which actually needs to be always visible) so that the reset time axis button always works, even when you have a large number of plots visible and you have scrolled down the list.</p>\n<p>\u2192 &lt;&lt;cset <a href=\"#!/labscript_suite/runviewer/commits/28c050d6343f\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">28c050d6343f</a>&gt;&gt;</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-05-01T00:48:40.554421+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Philip Starkey", "uuid": "{48af65db-e5fc-459c-a7eb-52eb1f9a5690}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B48af65db-e5fc-459c-a7eb-52eb1f9a5690%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://